00:35:04.688 --> 00:35:08.567 position:32.86%,start align:start size:42.38% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Garak promised me</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1169
00:35:08.567 --> 00:35:11.872 position:30.95%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Listen to me, Ziyal.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1170
00:35:15.665 --> 00:35:17.861 position:27.14%,start align:start size:53.81% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>He's never coming back.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1171
00:35:17.861 --> 00:35:19.604 position:55.71%,start align:start size:34.76% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>He's probably</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1172
00:35:17.861 --> 00:35:19.604 position:55.71%,start align:start size:34.76% line:84.62% 
