<c.white><c.mono_sans>Misery loves company.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1199
00:36:13.589 --> 00:36:15.308 position:48.10%,start align:start size:30.95% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>All my life</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1200
00:36:13.589 --> 00:36:15.308 position:48.10%,start align:start size:42.38% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I've done nothing</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1201
00:36:15.308 --> 00:36:17.274 position:48.10%,start align:start size:42.38% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but try to please</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1202
00:36:15.308 --> 00:36:17.274 position:48.10%,start align:start size:27.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>that man.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1203
00:36:17.274 --> 00:36:18.507 position:42.38%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I let him mold me...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1204
00:36:18.507 --> 00:36:21.106 position:30.95%,start align:start size:48.10% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>let him turn me into</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1205
00:36:18.507 --> 00:36:21.106 position:30.95%,start align:start size:59.52% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>a mirror image of himself.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1206
00:36:21.106 --> 00:36:22.945 position:34.76%,start align:start size:55.71% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And how did he repay me?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1207
00:36:22.945 --> 00:36:23.905 position:59.52%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>With exile.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1208
00:36:23.905 --> 00:36:25.225 position:46.19%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But I forgave him.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1209
00:36:25.225 --> 00:36:27.985 position:40.48%,start align:start size:50.00% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And here, in the end,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1210
00:36:25.225 --> 00:36:27.985 position:40.48%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I thought maybe,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1211
00:36:27.985 --> 00:36:31.102 position:48.10%,start align:start size:36.67% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>just maybe, he</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1212
00:36:27.985 --> 00:36:31.102 position:48.10%,start align:start size:42.38% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>could forgive me.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1213
00:36:33.222 --> 00:36:35.223 position:19.52%,start align:start size:59.52% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>From what I've seen of him</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1214
00:36:33.222 --> 00:36:35.223 position:19.52%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>over the past month,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1215
00:36:35.223 --> 00:36:37.501 position:19.52%,start align:start size:51.90% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>he doesn't come across</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1216
00:36:35.223 --> 00:36:37.501 position:19.52%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>as the forgiving type.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1217
00:36:37.501 --> 00:36:38.861 position:48.10%,start align:start size:42.38% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I've been a fool.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

