00:36:40.819 --> 00:36:43.180 position:32.86%,start align:start size:57.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>one I can ever teach you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1222
00:36:43.180 --> 00:36:46.498 position:32.86%,start align:start size:57.62% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Sentiment is the greatest</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1223
00:36:43.180 --> 00:36:46.498 position:32.86%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>weakness of all.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1224
00:36:46.498 --> 00:36:49.777 position:19.52%,start align:start size:38.57% line:73.96% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>If that's true,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1225
00:36:46.498 --> 00:36:49.777 position:19.52%,start align:start size:42.38% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>it's a lesson I'd</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1226
00:36:46.498 --> 00:36:49.777 position:19.52%,start align:start size:42.38% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>rather not learn.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1227
00:36:49.777 --> 00:36:51.817 position:36.67%,start align:start size:36.67% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>(</c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans><i> door opens</i></c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans> )</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1228
00:36:54.616 --> 00:36:56.576 position:27.14%,start align:start size:55.71% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>you might want to know--</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1229
00:36:54.616 --> 00:36:56.576 position:40.48%,start align:start size:27.14% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I thought</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1230
00:36:56.576 --> 00:37:00.544 position:30.95%,start align:start size:48.10% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>if you wish to speak</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1231
00:36:56.576 --> 00:37:00.544 position:30.95%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to Tain... do it now,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1232
00:37:00.544 --> 00:37:01.534 position:29.05%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>before it's too late.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

