00:37:23.768 --> 00:37:25.407 position:32.86%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Elim, is that you?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1235
00:37:25.407 --> 00:37:26.725 position:42.38%,start align:start size:25.24% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>It's me.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1236
00:37:28.326 --> 00:37:31.125 position:27.14%,start align:start size:53.81% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Everything's gone dark.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1237
00:37:31.125 --> 00:37:33.205 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I can't see you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1238
00:37:34.924 --> 00:37:36.604 position:36.67%,start align:start size:36.67% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Are you alone?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1239
00:37:37.883 --> 00:37:38.923 position:34.76%,start align:start size:17.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Yes.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

