1243
00:37:49.520 --> 00:37:51.359 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>they can't be trusted.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1244
00:37:51.359 --> 00:37:53.278 position:34.76%,start align:start size:55.71% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>They must be dealt with.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1245
00:37:53.278 --> 00:37:55.198 position:32.86%,start align:start size:44.29% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I've already taken</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1246
00:37:53.278 --> 00:37:55.198 position:38.57%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>care of it.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

