00:37:55.198 --> 00:38:00.476 position:25.24%,start align:start size:59.52% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And what about Gul Vorlem?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1248
00:38:00.476 --> 00:38:02.595 position:21.43%,start align:start size:65.24% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Were you able to contact him?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1249
00:38:02.595 --> 00:38:04.154 position:40.48%,start align:start size:29.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Years ago.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1250
00:38:04.154 --> 00:38:06.274 position:27.14%,start align:start size:53.81% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>The Romulan ambassador?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1251
00:38:06.274 --> 00:38:07.234 position:19.52%,start align:start size:29.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>He's gone.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1252
