<c.white><c.mono_sans>All your enemies are dead.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1253
00:38:11.233 --> 00:38:13.730 position:44.29%,start align:start size:19.52% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Good.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1254
00:38:13.730 --> 00:38:17.151 position:23.33%,start align:start size:61.43% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>his enemies to outlive him.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1255
00:38:13.730 --> 00:38:17.151 position:29.05%,start align:start size:50.00% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>A man shouldn't allow</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1256
