1257
00:38:19.470 --> 00:38:21.150 position:19.52%,start align:start size:29.05% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Unless you</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1258
00:38:19.470 --> 00:38:21.150 position:19.52%,start align:start size:36.67% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>still consider</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1259
00:38:21.150 --> 00:38:23.389 position:19.52%,start align:start size:36.67% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>me your enemy.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1260
00:38:23.389 --> 00:38:24.989 position:57.62%,start align:start size:23.33% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Elim...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1261
00:38:24.989 --> 00:38:27.228 position:29.05%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>promise me one thing.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1262
