<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'm listening.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1263
00:38:28.627 --> 00:38:31.547 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Don't die here.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

