00:38:31.547 --> 00:38:34.146 position:36.67%,start align:start size:34.76% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Escape. Live.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1265
00:38:34.146 --> 00:38:35.785 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Let me guess...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1266
00:38:35.785 --> 00:38:37.985 position:32.86%,start align:start size:44.29% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>so that I can make</c.mono_sans></c.white>

