00:38:35.785 --> 00:38:37.985 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>the Dominion pay</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1268
00:38:37.985 --> 00:38:40.648 position:21.43%,start align:start size:65.24% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>for what they've done to you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1269
