<c.white><c.mono_sans>You wouldn't deny an old man</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1270
00:38:40.648 --> 00:38:44.983 position:27.14%,start align:start size:53.81% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>his revenge, would you?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1271
00:38:44.983 --> 00:38:47.902 position:32.86%,start align:start size:46.19% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'll do as you ask,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

